headline: Costco Expands Instacart In Europe As Valuation Stays Above Fair Value
summary: Costco Wholesale expanded its Instacart partnership to introduce same-day delivery in France and Spain. The company rolled out Clean Cult’s sustainable laundry detergent sheets nationwide across its U.S. warehouses. These moves extend Costco’s digital reach in Europe and add an eco-focused product to its household essentials lineup.
